<item rdf:about="http://www.anthonyrkarnowski.com/journal/archives/2007_08.html#001274">
<title></title>
<link>http://www.anthonyrkarnowski.com/journal/archives/2007_08.html#001274</link>
<description><![CDATA[<p>Not too much to report today. I've made a bit more progress on the first book of the Myths of Thera, but otherwise all is quiet on the writing front. I've spent the morning continuing my reread of the Harry Potter series (I started on Goblet this morning). Soon I will be heading out to teach some people how to play the drums. I never really saw myself teaching, but at about a year and a half in I'm still digging it immensely.</p>

<p>Anyway, I'll write again if/when I have something else to talk about. This entry was mainly an attempt to keep myself blogging. It's been a while since I've done it consistently, and I really need to get back into the habit.</p>

<p>Until next time...</p>]]></description>
<dc:subject>General</dc:subject>
<dc:creator>anthony</dc:creator>
